WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Well, if the masses are equal, there's no way to favor one

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.000
direction out of the other--it'll remain motionless.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:09.000
If M₁ is bigger, it's going to go downwards--so that would be counterclockwise.

00:00:09.000 --> 99:59:59.000
And if M₁ is smaller, then M₂ will tend to go down--that's clockwise and there we go.

